## Removing Lens Caps

!Removing Lens Caps

## Attaching Lens Hoods

When attached, lens hoods reduce glare and protect the front lens element.

!Attaching Lens Hoods

> ⚠️ **Note:**  
> Be sure to rotate the hood to the final position.
